title: Uber 000-005 (+ 24 Variant Covers|Avatar|2013|Dgtl-HR|JK-Empire)
description:
The previous single-issue torrents from Darkness-Empire were traditionally scanned throughout, whereas these are this week's digital re-releases by JK-Empire. Only marginally higher resolution, but significantly crisper texture, as one might expect.

Included are the full sets of variants from those Darkness-Empire scans, plus some separately posted additional covers ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8764940" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8764940</a>  ), thus allowing for a wholesale replacement of these versions for the non-digital ones.
